data.description: Discover the epitome of luxury in this 4-bed, 3.5-bath gem within the esteemed Trafalgar Villages community. What sets this home apart? Not one, but two master bedrooms! The first-floor Master Suite pampers you with dual sinks, a garden tub, and spacious walk-in closets, while upstairs, the second master bedroom offers privacy and convenience.    Inside, gleaming tile floors in the kitchen create a sleek look, while plush carpets make every room cozy. You'll love the elegance of granite countertops in the kitchen and bathrooms. Step outside to your covered lanai, your private sanctuary for relaxation or hosting guests.    Location couldn't be better with dining, shopping, hospitals, and attractions just moments away. Whether you're a buyer or investor, this property offers unmatched convenience.    Don't wait! Act now to schedule an in-person tour and see this elite community for yourself. Plus, with the HOA covering lawn care, garbage pickup, and pest control, and 24 hour guarded front gate , securing your paradise has never been easier. Seize this opportunity today!
